Contexte projet et hypothèse pour Google Ads :

{
  "project_id": "proj-123",
  "hypothesis_id": "hypo-001",
  "startup_context": {
    "mission": "Aider les TPE à automatiser leurs tâches",
    "value_proposition": "Une solution simple et abordable d’automatisation",
    "pain_points": ["perte de temps", "tâches répétitives"],
    "market_type": "B2B",
    "target_segments": ["dirigeants TPE", "indépendants"],
    "known_competitors": ["Zapier", "Make"]
  },
  "offer": {
    "product_name": "Alpes Automate",
    "key_benefits": ["gain de temps", "simplicité", "tarif abordable"],
    "trial_or_demo": "oui"
  },
  "goal": "leads",
  "landing_url": "https://exemple.com/demo",
  "geo": { "countries": ["FR"] },
  "constraints": {
    "daily_budget_eur": 20,
    "must_include_keywords": ["automatisation PME", "logiciel tâches"],
    "forbidden_terms": ["gratuit", "emploi"]
  },
  "utm": {
    "utm_campaign": "bootcamp_alpact_h1",
    "utm_content": "varA"
  },
  "timeline": {
    "start_date": "2025-09-10",
    "end_date": "2025-09-24"
  }
}

Veuillez retourner uniquement l’objet JSON valide selon le schéma défini par le System Prompt.

